	<h2 class="pageheader">About</h2>
	
	<p>This site is perfect for a small artist or designer wishing to show case their work. It runs its data from XML rather than MySQL to cut down on overhead costs and also to simplify the setting up of the site.</p>

	<p>When pictures are uploaded they are reduced in size to three versions: a large version for lightbox viewing with max qulaity settings, a medium size version for display on the main page at lower quality, and a thumbnail version for use in the admin interface.</p>
	
